'''Isaggn''' tga yat tqbilt zɣ tiabilin n tamunt n tiabilin n [[Ayt Ṣwab]]. Tg ula yat zɣ lmacixat n tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]], tḍfar i tagrawt n [[Awgnz]], tanbaḍt n Wactukn-Ayt Baha, tsga n [[Tasga n Sus-Massa|Sus-Massa]]. 

Ar ittini usiḍn lli ittyuskar ɣ usggʷas n 2004 mas macixa ad zdɣn gis kran 1025 n middn d 290 n tawjiwin<ref>'''( fr + ar )''' [https://www.webcitation.org/678NyvGs8?url=http://www.lavieeco.com/documents_officiels/Recensement%20population.pdf Asiḍn n n imzdaɣn n Lmɣrib ɣ usggas n 2004] <small>( PDF ) -</small> Tasmirit tamattayt n usɣiws.</ref>.

